dcterms:description: A small-scale dataset used for evaluating unsupervised open domain recognition. The target domain consists of 50 animal classes with 37,322 images, while the source domain contains 2,970 images collected via Google image search. The knowledge database used is WordNet.
dcterms:title: I2AwA

dcterms:description: A large-scale dataset used for evaluating unsupervised open domain recognition. The source domain is ILSVRC-2012 with 1,000 classes and 1,279,847 images, while the target domain is the validation set of WebVision with 5,000 classes and 294,009 images. The knowledge database used is WordNet.
dcterms:title: I2WebV
